# CODEOWNERS — chỉ có tác dụng nếu repo bật được branch protection (plan trả phí).
# Repo private GitHub Free: file này là tài liệu tham khảo cho team.
#
# Format: <pattern>  @github-username-or-team
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default — Lead/Sub-lead review tất cả
*                           @lead-github-username

# Solution docs — Sub-lead review
docs/solutions/             @sublead-github-username

# Database migrations — Lead review (impact cao)
src/main/resources/migration/   @lead-github-username

# CI/CD — Lead review
.github/                    @lead-github-username
